@startuml

actor Usuario
participant Browser
participant Nginx
participant "Gunicorn (WSGI)" as Gunicorn
participant "Django App" as Django
participant Database

Usuario -> Browser: Ingresa URL / acción HTTP
Browser -> Nginx: HTTP Request (GET/POST)

Nginx -> Nginx: Evalúa request (static? cache? routing)

alt Request estático
    Nginx -> Browser: Devuelve archivo estático
else Request dinámico
    Nginx -> Gunicorn: Forward request (WSGI)
    
    Gunicorn -> Django: Invoca aplicación (callable WSGI)
    
    Django -> Django: Middleware processing
    Django -> Django: URL routing
    Django -> Django: View logic
    
    Django -> Database: Query (ORM)
    Database -> Django: Resultados
    
    Django -> Django: Render template / JSON
    Django -> Gunicorn: Response HTTP
    
    Gunicorn -> Nginx: Response
    Nginx -> Browser: HTTP Response
end alt

Browser -> Usuario: Renderiza respuesta

@enduml
